We also have outdated medical care. Other countries no longer have diseases or even things like the flu. They don't want us to visit them so a ban is in place. They are scared of us. 
We are now trying to catch up to the rest of the world.
 We're told that in order to trade or be allowed to travel worldwide that we'll have to become more advanced. The problem with that is that we're so far behind that we'll never catch up. 
The government has decided to make a deal with the devil.

We also have outdated medical care. Other countries no longer have diseases or even things like the flu. They don't want us to visit them so a ban is in place. They are scared of us. 
We are now trying to catch up to the rest of the world.
 We're told that in order to trade or be allowed to travel worldwide that we'll have to become more advanced. The problem with that is that we're so far behind that we'll never catch up. 
The government has decided to make a deal with the devil.
 That's the only option to even have a chance in this new world. The devil will make our country as advanced as the rest of the world but it requires the souls of everyone in the United States. 
The government has decided that it's a good idea.

No one knows but this war is about that very thing.

We also have outdated medical care. Other countries no longer have diseases or even things like the flu. They don't want us to visit them so a ban is in place. They are scared of us. 
We are now trying to catch up to the rest of the world.
 We're told that in order to trade or be allowed to travel worldwide that we'll have to become more advanced. The problem with that is that we're so far behind that we'll never catch up. 
The government has decided to make a deal with the devil.
 That's the only option to even have a chance in this new world. The devil will make our country as advanced as the rest of the world but it requires the souls of everyone in the United States. 
The government has decided that it's a good idea.
